aṅguttara nikāya 11
paṭhamapaṇṇāsaka
sāmaññavagga
an 11.502–981
ekādasahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato gopālako bhabbo gogaṇaṃ pariharituṃ phātikātuṃ.
katamehi ekādasahi?
idha, bhikkhave, gopālako rūpaññū hoti… pe…
evameva kho, bhikkhave, ekādasahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo cakkhusmiṃ aniccānupassī viharituṃ…
pe…
paṭinissaggānupassī viharitunti.
